#

Savory Teriyaki Salmon with Cauliflower Rice

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinLow-CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

Asian CuisineHealthyDinnerProtein-Packed

Description

A delectable salmon fillet glazed with homemade teriyaki, served over fluffy cauliflower rice for a low-carb, high-protein delight.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 6 oz
  • Soy sauce (low sodium): 1/4 cup
  • Honey: 2 tbsp
  • Rice vinegar: 1 tbsp
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Ginger (grated): 1 tbsp
  • Cauliflower (riced): 2 cups
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
  • Green onions (sliced): 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
